data.description: This lovely home is back on the market.  It is not due to any fault of the seller.It is getting a new roof.  Electrical and plumbing issues have been repaired.  There was a sewer cope and it is in great shape.  This house is ready to move into.  Carpets will be cleaned prior to closing.  Back deck is also getting scraped and painted.  All the work is completed for your buyer.Charming bungalow with a few sweet surprises.  There is a work shop attached to the garage for all those projects on your list, there is a wood burning stove in the spacious family room, for those cozy evenings and a hidden washer/dryer area conveniently  located!   Close to UNC, shopping, churches and a park.  Swamp cooler included for those hot summer days.Don't miss the opportunity to own your own home!!
